或者在串流平台上享用香港地區的內容。大部分平台例如 ViuTV，Netflix 和 Disney+ 甚至 YouTube 都可以用這個方式達到效果，使用體驗上與香港觀衆一樣，登入相關平台就可以看到這些本地專屬內容。不過需要注意的是並非所有 VPN 服務都可以提供穩定的速度來進行順暢的媒體播放，因此在選擇 VPN 的時候就要留意，以免因小失大。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1086304" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Screenshot-2022-02-14-at-5.34.11-PM.jpg" alt="" width="2542" height="1662" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Screenshot-2022-02-14-at-5.34.11-PM.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Screenshot-2022-02-14-at-5.34.11-PM-694x454.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Screenshot-2022-02-14-at-5.34.11-PM-1280x837.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Screenshot-2022-02-14-at-5.34.11-PM-768x502.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Screenshot-2022-02-14-at-5.34.11-PM-1536x1004.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Screenshot-2022-02-14-at-5.34.11-PM-2048x1339.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" />▲ 香港區 Netflix 有熟悉的吉卜力動畫系列兼字幕齊全，到了海外不一定能看到</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1086464" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/signal-2022-02-15-213410_001-scaled.jpeg" alt="" width="2560" height="1399" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/signal-2022-02-15-213410_001-scaled.jpeg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/signal-2022-02-15-213410_001-694x379.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/signal-2022-02-15-213410_001-1280x700.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/signal-2022-02-15-213410_001-768x420.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/signal-2022-02-15-213410_001-1536x839.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/signal-2022-02-15-213410_001-2048x1119.jpeg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" />▲ 可以即時看香港電視台甚至與其他觀衆互動</p><h2>Surfshark 簡單使用易上手</h2><p>在衆多 VPN 服務之中，<a href="https://get.surfshark.net/aff_c?offer_id=87&amp;aff_id=4476&amp;url_id=1171">Surfshark</a> 可說是相當有名的一個，除了信譽良好外，其速度和穩定性也備受認可，除了可以輕鬆應付媒體串流外，就算 P2P 下載也不成問題。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1086305" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Screenshot-2022-02-14-at-5.40.20-PM.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="402" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Screenshot-2022-02-14-at-5.40.20-PM.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Screenshot-2022-02-14-at-5.40.20-PM-694x174.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Screenshot-2022-02-14-at-5.40.20-PM-1280x322.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Screenshot-2022-02-14-at-5.40.20-PM-768x193.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Screenshot-2022-02-14-at-5.40.20-PM-1536x386.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Screenshot-2022-02-14-at-5.40.20-PM-2048x515.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" />▲ 各區伺服器速度都有不錯表現</p><p>對於擔心設定麻煩的朋友來說，Surfshark VPN 亦為不同的系統和裝置都提供了專用的 App，安裝後只需要登入就可以自動完成設定，無需自己進行繁複的網絡設定，輕鬆上手。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1075450 size-large" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Screenshot-2021-12-11-at-12.52.45-AM-1280x802.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="802" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Screenshot-2021-12-11-at-12.52.45-AM-1280x802.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Screenshot-2021-12-11-at-12.52.45-AM-694x435.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Screenshot-2021-12-11-at-12.52.45-AM-768x481.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Screenshot-2021-12-11-at-12.52.45-AM-1536x962.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Screenshot-2021-12-11-at-12.52.45-AM-2048x1282.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Screenshot-2021-12-11-at-12.52.45-AM.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" />▲ 提供不同系統的專用 App</p><h2>提升網絡私隱保障</h2><p>VPN 服務作為海外媒體串流工具自然好用，不過其實還有一個實用的功能，就是透過 VPN 來上網，原來可以隱藏自己的網絡 IP，達到進一步保障私隱的效果。現在不少網站都有使用追蹤技術來記錄用家的網上活動，網絡 IP 就是其中一個常見方式，而且普通的瀏覽器設定並不能阻擋這樣的追蹤，VPN 就是唯一的解決辦法。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-976806 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Untitled-1.jpg" alt="" width="1337" height="850" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Untitled-1.jpg 1337w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Untitled-1-694x441.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Untitled-1-1280x814.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Untitled-1-768x488.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" />▲ 可在 App 上輕鬆設定安全功能</p><p>Surfshark VPN 更提供了 Kill Switch 功能，一旦裝置和 VPN 連線失效，就會直接停止所有連線，避免資料在未經 VPN 保護之下流出。Surfshark 也提供 Multihop 功能，可以連接兩個地區的 VPN，進一步繞道令追蹤變得困難。</p><h2>82% 優惠入手時機</h2><p>現在 Surfshark 整提供虎年優惠，訂閱 24 個月可獲得 83% 折扣，另外再獲贈 2 個月免費使用，每月只需要 HK$17.63。他們特別之處是容許無限同時連接，也就是就算與家人好友共用帳戶，也不怕影響其他人，大家夾錢訂購服務就更加抵用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1086314" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1200x628-Traditional-Chinese-google-1.jpg" alt="" width="2400" height="1256" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1200x628-Traditional-Chinese-google-1.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1200x628-Traditional-Chinese-google-1-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1200x628-Traditional-Chinese-google-1-1280x670.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1200x628-Traditional-Chinese-google-1-768x402.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/1200x